; epsilon tall, narrow, with equal short horizontals; theta and omicron are rhomboid; mu has vertical first and last, with the diagonals starting below the top and only desencing to the mid-point; nu is similar; rho has small curved, closed loop; sigma is lunate but rectilinear, with very short horizontals.",[46,53],{"type":47,"l":48,"from":49,"to":50,"h":51,"unit":52,"atLeast":51,"atMost":51},"letterHeight","Line 1-2","line1","line2","110","mm",{"type":54,"l":55,"from":49,"to":50,"h":56,"unit":52,"atLeast":56,"atMost":56},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","20",{"_":58,"notBefore":59,"notAfter":60,"evidence":61},"Dated by reference to Flavius Martinianos, consularis of Sicily between 352 and 358 CE (Soraci)",352,358,"prosopography",[63,68],{"_":64,"type":65,"ref":66,"region":67},"Agrigentum","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462086","Sicilia",{"_":8,"type":69,"ref":70,"region":67},"modern","http://sws.geonames.org/6541860",[72],[73,74],37.32084,13.58876,[76,77],37.297649,13.591579,"Sicily",{"_":4,"role":3,"ref":5},{"type":81},"inventory",{"_":83,"mainLang":84,"languages":85},"Ancient Greek","grc",[83],{"n":87,"url":88,"height":89,"width":90,"desc":6,"surfaceType":91},"screen","ISic001830_tiled.tif","5520px","3680px","front",[93,95],{"atLeast":94,"atMost":94},110,{"atLeast":96,"atMost":96},20,[98],"Caminneci, Parello, Soraci, 2023, Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento",[100],"A7HRWIUH",[102,103,104,25,29,33,105,106,107,108,106,109,110,84],"isic001830","building inscription of martinianos",{"_":22},"agrigentum","agrigento","sicilia","sicily","parco archeologico valle dei templi","ancient greek","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φλάβιος Μαρτεινιανός\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\